  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hostile creatures are invading the enchanted meadows!</strong> <strong>Help the trolls defend their basket, which contains precious items.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build your defense</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant trees to prevent the  creatures from reaching the basket. The trees have different strengths, so plant them strategically. Collect coins from defeated creatures to be able to afford more trees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/c5fd0d3eac2bb7fa7fc9a54148c52df5.poster.avif?t=1767003469\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/c5fd0d3eac2bb7fa7fc9a54148c52df5.webm?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/c5fd0d3eac2bb7fa7fc9a54148c52df5.mp4?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Assist your trees</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use different abilities to help your trees defend against the creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/f64285b0da579787461c05b69904bcc3.poster.avif?t=1767003469\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/f64285b0da579787461c05b69904bcc3.webm?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/f64285b0da579787461c05b69904bcc3.mp4?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade your trees</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stand on your trees to increase their level and make them stronger, so they're able to defeat even the strongest creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/ddc630885102fe616d4aa2f8c13015d9.poster.avif?t=1767003469\" width=616 height=203 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/ddc630885102fe616d4aa2f8c13015d9.webm?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Defeat powerful bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use all you've got to defend against the boss creatures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/77cca10b4a4490df3a7391c9a899b9ad.poster.avif?t=1767003469\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/77cca10b4a4490df3a7391c9a899b9ad.webm?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/77cca10b4a4490df3a7391c9a899b9ad.mp4?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your basket in 20 different levels, through spring, summer, autumn and winter.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock the random mode to play levels with randomly generated waves, for replayability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can be played by 1 or 2 players (co-op).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports mouse and gamepads (Xbox / PlayStation / Nintendo).</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hostile creatures are invading the enchanted meadows!</strong> <strong>Help the trolls defend their basket, which contains precious items.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build your defense</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant trees to prevent the  creatures from reaching the basket. The trees have different strengths, so plant them strategically. Collect coins from defeated creatures to be able to afford more trees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/c5fd0d3eac2bb7fa7fc9a54148c52df5.poster.avif?t=1767003469\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/c5fd0d3eac2bb7fa7fc9a54148c52df5.webm?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/c5fd0d3eac2bb7fa7fc9a54148c52df5.mp4?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Assist your trees</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use different abilities to help your trees defend against the creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/f64285b0da579787461c05b69904bcc3.poster.avif?t=1767003469\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/f64285b0da579787461c05b69904bcc3.webm?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3651630/extras/f64285b0da579787461c05b69904bcc3.mp4?t=1767003469\" type=\"video/